description.en: HollyGold(HGOLD) allows you to become part of the next major Hollywood Motion Picture Production.  When you purchasse in HollyGold(HGOLD), you enter the magical world of movies!  HollyGold’s team members and its advisory team have produced and/or provided production services for over 1600 films including  Oscar and Emmy award winning films as well as many Blokckbuster hits.
